# YellowStone Client Onboarding Form

A professional, client-facing onboarding form built for YellowStone PMS 
implementation by RBS. Sent to new clients to collect all information 
required before their implementation begins.

## What It Does

Guides new YellowStone clients through a structured 11-section onboarding 
form covering everything the implementation team needs to configure their 
system from day one. Built as a single HTML file — no installation, no 
dependencies, works in any browser.

## Sections

1. **Yellowstone Users** — Collect names and emails for all platform users
2. **Business Information** — Legal name, address, phone, correspondence email
3. **Business Email Templates** — Collect or note standardized customer emails
4. **Reservation Types** — Types, check-in/out times, nights, included meals
5. **Activities** — Bookable activities, times, and on-property locations
6. **Lodging & Rooms** — Locations, room names, capacity, and room types
7. **Pricing & Rates** — Deposits, tax rates, gratuity, rates list, cancellation policy
8. **Memberships** — Membership tiers, fees, and renewal frequency
9. **Guides & Employees** — Staff directory with titles and contact info
10. **Guests** — Existing guest list via CSV upload
11. **Notes** — General comments, questions for the Implementation Manager, preferred contact method

## Features

- Sticky progress bar with clickable section navigation
- All sections collapsible and expandable
- Dynamic row entry for users, staff, rooms, rates, and more
- Smart conditional fields — answer boxes appear or hide based on selections
- Custom pill-style meal multi-select for reservation types
- CSV file upload for guest list import
- ADA / WCAG 2.1 compliant — keyboard navigable, screen reader friendly
- RBS and YellowStone dual branding throughout
- Mobile responsive
- Success confirmation screen on submit

